---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 129
By: St Alphonsus Liguori
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Sacrifice and Suffering=Knowledge Through Chastisement
---
Contradiction, sickness, scruples, spiritual aridity, and all inner and
outward torments are the chisel with which God carves his statues for
paradise.
